OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,FSecretary of State for Health and
OL,7,FSocial Care Wes Streeting has spoken
OL,8,Fabout the challenges and pressures
OL,9,Ffacing the NHS in Cumbria as he set
OL,10,Fout the Government's long-term vision
OL,11,Fto reform social care.
OL,13,FThe Labour MP visited Carlisle as he
OL,14,Fannounced new plans regarding social
OL,15,Fcare, with long-term funding and
OL,16,Freform not expected to be delivered
OL,17,Funtil 2028.
