OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,FIt comes as ministers announced the
OL,7,Ffirst steps to creating a National
OL,8,FCare Service, with an independent
OL,9,Fcommission expected to begin work this
OL,10,Fspring.
OL,12,FWhen asked about the pressures seen in
OL,13,Fthe NHS this winter, Streeting spoke
OL,14,Fof the challenges faced by many A&E
OL,15,Fdepartments throughout the country,
OL,16,Fincluding in Cumbria.
OL,18,FHe said: "I think people have seen
OL,19,Fthroughout this winter, particularly
OL,20,Facross Cumbria pressures in our
OL,21,Femergency departments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
