OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,F"There are people on trolleys in
OL,7,Fcorridors, I will be off to the West
OL,8,FCumberland Hospital later today to
OL,9,Ftalk through the pressures with the
OL,10,Fstaff. I think the winter crisis we
OL,11,Fsee in the NHS is exactly why we need
OL,12,Fto grasp the nettle of big long term
OL,13,Freforms to social care that is needed
OL,14,Fbecause as well as our 10 year plan
OL,15,Ffor the NHS we also need to reform our
OL,16,Fsocial care.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
