OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F351A1735912436
OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,F"One of the reasons why we see A&E
OL,7,Fdepartments so busy is because we
OL,8,Fcan't get people out of hospital beds
OL,9,Fand back into the community because of
OL,10,Fa lack of social care. That is why
OL,11,Fthis government is doing things
OL,12,Fdifferently."
OL,14,FStreeting said the pressures seen in
OL,15,Fthe NHS this winter is why his
OL,16,FGovernment is making changes to social
OL,17,Fcare.
