OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,FHe said: "The crisis we have seen in
OL,7,Four NHS this winter, not just in
OL,8,FCumbria but right across the country
OL,9,Fis exactly why this government is
OL,10,Ftaking the big reform decisions now to
OL,11,Fhelp our NHS and social care services.
OL,13,F"Whether that is the huge injection of
OL,14,Ffunding in the budget or specific
OL,15,Fmeasures like the disabled facilities
OL,16,Fgrant. There are lots we are doing
OL,17,Fright now but we have also got to make
OL,18,Fthe right long term reform decisions
OL,19,Fon the NHS and on social care.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
