OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,F"By the end of this parliament I think
OL,7,Fpeople will see Britain in a better
OL,8,Fplace than the Labour Government found
OL,9,Fit when we came in but I also think we
OL,10,Fwill have established the right long
OL,11,Fterm plan for the country.
OL,13,F"People will judge us on results, we
OL,14,Fknow that and we are determined to
OL,15,Fdeliver."
OL,17,FAs part of the announcement today,
OL,18,FStreeting has provided an extra #86
OL,19,Fmillion to the disabled facilities
OL,20,Fgrant.
