OL,3,CSecretary of State for Health speaks
OL,4,Cabout NHS challenges in Cumbria
OL,6,FHe said: "Today we are announcing an
OL,7,Fuplift in the disabled facilities
OL,8,Fgrant of #86 million.
OL,10,F"We announced the uplift in the budget
OL,11,Fin April but we are announcing that
OL,12,Fextra cash right now to help people.
OL,13,FWe are going to see the success of
OL,14,Fthis with one family in Carlisle and
OL,15,Fwe are releasing that cash to benefit
OL,16,Fpeople right across the country."
